{
  "stem": "2581.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in a way, that was the only time-- it lasted about four weeks-- where I had enough to eat and I was-- felt real good about myself.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I says, gee, I'm going to overcome this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when you feel good, you think about your father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I would bring in some food by the end of the day for my father.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One time-- second time, third time, one of the time I came in-- I says-- I says, Dad, maybe I should stay here with you overnight.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you shouldn't be alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I stayed overnight.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never got up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never heard of a-- of a sickness to catch you so suddenly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It must've been that there was-- these lice that were crawling all over there, must've been on me for some time that I got the sickness.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I never got up from there till the end of-- till we were deported.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were taken out from this Lager Four till in April, when we-- when this camp was liquidated and we were sent to Lager One for the deportation-- for-- for transportation from there to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was called their medical-- what do they call it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lavier.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lavier?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember what it was called, really.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Revier.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Revier.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's what it is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Krankenrevier.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was really nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, they couldn't have given you-- not even aspirin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they could give you compresses or tell you what it is, or try to help you in any primitive way that he could.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But there were no medications.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, people tried to stay away because those were the first ones that were taken out to make room for others.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You tried to stay away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People didn't go there.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
